dialogueLines.line: Agh. Okay okay FINE. I admit defeat.
dialogueLines.speaker: prisma

dialogueLines.line: To think I'd be defeated by a mere mermaid..
dialogueLines.speaker: prisma

dialogueLines.line: Like it matters... I'll leave you be and revert all of this back to normal.
dialogueLines.speaker: prisma

dialogueLines.line: *Cod* to be caught up in all of this mess!

dialogueLines.line: Ya' know, they *shore* did remind me of a Glass catfish (Kryptopterus vitreolus)

dialogueLines.line: OK, I have no idea how you escaped your tank but you're coming back with me.
dialogueLines.speaker: ko

dialogueLines.line: WHAT IS THE MEANING OF THIS! TURN ME BACK!
dialogueLines.speaker: prisma

dialogueLines.line: Wh- Who in *cod*'s name are you?

dialogueLines.line: ...Not important but just forget we ever met, Atlanta.
